pickup the egg on top of the cupboard
turn left and move towards the microwave oven
put the egg in the microwave oven and boil it for five minutes
take out the egg and turn right towards the sink
drop the egg in the sink

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the egg on the counter, behind the sponge.
Turn to your left and go to the microwave.
Cook the egg in the microwave.
Turn around and go left, to the sink.
Place the egg in the right bottom corner of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked egg in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, head towards the stove, turn left towards the end of the counter.
Pick up the egg from the counter.
Turn left and walk towards the microwave on your left.
Open the microwave, place the egg in it, heat it up, and take the egg out of microwave.
Turn right and head towards the sink.
Place the egg in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm egg in the sink.
